fields.search:
select place, avg(value) 
from default.bhci_opiods 
WHERE year = 2013 
   AND indicator = 'Opioid-Related Unintentional Drug Overdose Mortality Rate (Age-Adjusted; Per 100,000 people)' 
   AND sex = 'Both' 
   AND race_ethnicity = 'All' 
  GROUP BY place
  ORDER BY place 
  LIMIT 10;
